					<head>Pentateuch</head>
					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/n79066420" rend="visible">
						<summary>Pentateuch and Hafṭarot provided with vowel-points, the Hafṭarot are also accentuated. </summary>
						<textLang mainLang="he">Hebrew</textLang>
						<msItem n="0" rend="v" class="lccn.loc.gov/n79066420">
							<locus from="1r" to="201v"/>
							<title xml:lang="en">Torah ṿe-hafṭarot </title>
							<title xml:lang="he">תורה והפטרות </title>
							<textLang mainLang="he">Hebrew</textLang>
							<decoNote type="marginal">
								<locus n="10r"/>A sketch of the candlestick.</decoNote>
							<note>
								<p>The Pentateuch is incomplete, lacking Genesis and several chapters of the rest of the books.</p>
								<p>Hafṭarot of the weekly portions and of the feasts and fasts:  folio144r. Before the benedictions at the beginning of a weekly Hafṭarah there is the sentence: <q>גאלינו יהוה צבאות שמו קדוש ישראל</q>.</p>
								<p>Folios 138v-140r give three certificates for a shoḥet in different Italian cursive hands, the second gives the date: <date calendar="Hebrew">5248</date> (<date calendar="Gregorian">1488</date>).</p>
								<p>This copy of the Pentateuch was probably intended as a pattern for the scribe of Sefer Torah, each verso beginning with the letter ו and forming with the following recto a column of 48 lines.</p>
								<p>The use of vowel-points and accents show inconsistency.</p>
							</note>
							<filiation>The manuscript shows affinity to Arundel Or 2 ( <ref target="Margoliouth_1965" type="number">68</ref>) </filiation>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<title xml:lang="en">Exodus (from chapter 17:15 to ch. 40:8)</title>
								<locus from="1r" to="31r"/>
								<decoNote type="illustration">A sketch of the candlestick.<locus n="10r"/>
								</decoNote>
							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<locus from="31r" to="58v"/>
								<title xml:lang="en">Leviticus (begins with ch. 8:28)</title>
							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<locus from="58v" to="99v"/>
								<title xml:lang="en">Numbers (missing chapters 7:61-15:10)</title>
							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<locus from="99v" to="138v"/>
								<title xml:lang="en">Deuteronomy (missing chapters 23:10-27:12)</title>
							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<locus from="138v" to="140r"/>
								<title xml:lang="en">Three certificates for a shoḥet. </title>
							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Hafṭarot </title>
								<incipit xml:lang="he">אתחיל לכתוב ההפטרות בעזרת רוכב ערבות.<locus n="144r"/>
								</incipit>
								<locus from="144r" to="201v"/>
							</msItem>
						</msItem>
